@node "requ" "requ"
  INSTALLATION/REQUIREMENTS
  -------------------------


  As for requirements, you must be running WB2 or higher, since
Gadtools.library is needed, ASL is needed.
 Furthermore, this program uses the time-saving IFF.library  (which I'll
include with the archive if I'm allowed to).
  Lastly, you need ReqTools.library.

  Once the required libraries are in your libs: directory, just drag the icon
to wherever you want, and double click it.
@endnode

